Introduction

Kim Suhye is a South Korean singer under 143 Entertainment. She is a member of the girl group MADEIN, as well as it's pre debut sub unit LIMELIGHT.

In 2021, Suhye also gained recognition for her participation in the survival show My Teenage Girl, where she was sadly eliminated in episode 8.
